space <- read_csv(here("data", "space_launches.csv"))
## Rows: 5727 Columns: 11
##  Column specification 
## Delimiter: ","
## chr (9): tag, launch_date, type, variant, mission, agency, state_code, categ...
## dbl (2): JD, launch_year
## 
##  Use `spec()` to retrieve the full column specification for this data.
##  Specify the column types or set `show_col_types = FALSE` to quiet this message.
treemap(space,
            index=c("type","mission"),
            vSize="launch_year",
            type="index",
            palette = paletteer_d("ggprism::prism_light2"),
            bg.labels=c("white"),
            align.labels=list(
              c("center", "center"), 
              c("right", "bottom")),
        title = "Space is Super Cool!",
        fontcolor.labels = c("Magenta", "Orange"),
        border.col = c("pink"),
        border.lwds = c(1),
        fontfamily.title = "serif"
          ) 
## Warning in if (class(try(col2rgb(palette), silent = TRUE)) == "try-error")
## stop("color palette is not correct"): the condition has length > 1 and only the
## first element will be used
## Warning in if (class(try(col2rgb(bg.labels), silent = TRUE)) == "try-error")
## stop("Invalid bg.labels"): the condition has length > 1 and only the first
## element will be used

ggsave(here("R", "worst_graph_ever.jpg"), plot = last_plot())
